{"tid":2325470,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"美國版孔乙己","createTime":"2020-12-14T15:06:03.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-09T08:02:16.000Z","uid":78243,"like":23,"dislike":47,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"8e2221371b22c80092b726498e1e505d637c0476","tid":2325470,"uid":78243,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-14T15:06:03.000Z","msg":"愛侵力一到店，所有吃漢堡人便都看著他笑，有的叫道，「愛侵力，你臉上又添上新傷疤了！」他不回答，對櫃裡說，「巨無霸餐，要一個大薯條。」便排出九文大錢。他們又故意的高聲嚷道，「你一定又輸了選舉了！」愛侵力睜大眼睛說，「你怎麼這樣憑空污人清白&hellip;&hellip;」「什麼清白？我前天親眼見你輸了選舉了，被吊著打。」愛侵力便漲紅了臉，額上的青筋條條綻出，爭辯道，「落敗不能算窮輸&hellip;&hellip;落敗！&hellip;&hellip;舞弊的事，能算輸麼？」接連便是難懂的話，什麼「Deep State」，什麼「Fake News」之類，引得眾人都鬨笑起來：店內外充滿了快活的空氣。"},{"pid":"659ea48974d54988986aee67694b574da7133a84","tid":2325470,"uid":78243,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-14T15:08:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"95484df5f0f76582b0a110a7d595092326709cb6","tid":2325470,"uid":78243,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-14T15:09:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a44e15176663a25158758aa85ffc5923f8a5be47","tid":2325470,"uid":44285,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-14T15:12:29.000Z","msg":"唉屌 拉"},{"pid":"7d7826a74e534a8d5575ebb79cdbb3a4f78c4b66","tid":2325470,"uid":78243,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"a44e15176663a25158758aa85ffc5923f8a5be47","tid":2325470,"uid":44285,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-14T15:12:29.000Z","msg":"唉屌 拉"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-14T15:14:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"802a9c737f25dfd2583bbf1844410980734db852","tid":2325470,"uid":367153,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-14T15:23:54.000Z","msg":"拉"},{"pid":"29c85bf2db42180a9f45d5b420d3417fc7b0b6f1","tid":2325470,"uid":78243,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":